  <body>
    <main>
      <div id="install-nudge">
        <div class="content">
          <div>You can install RLComms - click install to see more!</div>
          <a href="/install" class="install">INSTALL</a>
          <a id="close-button" class="close">&#215;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="content">
          <h1>Installation:</h1>
          <p>
            <a href="/">Back to login</a>
          </p>
          
          <h2>iOS</h2>
          <p>
            Look for the share button in Safari, select "Add to Home Screen," and then just follow 
            the prompts.
          </p>
          <img src="https://cdn.glitch.global/4d3939de-7a6c-4907-91f2-457806b6567a/install-ios.png?v=1685890312619" alt="use the share functionality of mobile safari then add to home screen" class="install">
          
          <h2>Android</h2>
          <p>
            Look for the "More" menu. This is the "three dots" menu in Chrome but could be different 
            depending on your brpwser. Next, select "Add to Home Screen," and then just follow 
            the prompts.
          </p>
          
          <h2>Desktop</h2>
          <p>
            Different browsers work differently, but look for an install icon in the URL bar of your browser, click, and follow the prompts.
          </p>
          <img src="https://cdn.glitch.global/4d3939de-7a6c-4907-91f2-457806b6567a/install-desktop.png?v=1685890312306" alt="different browsers work differently, but look in your URL bar for an install icon" class="install">
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
